  <brief_title>Effects of Hypolipemic Treatment on Adipokines</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Effects of 90-day Monotherapies With Atorvastatin, Fenofibrate and Combined Therapy With Atorvastatin and Fenofibrate on Lipid Profile, Fasting Plasma Glucose, Proinflammatory Cytokines and Adipokines</official_title>
