  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study is planned to show whether monotherapies or combined hypolipemic therapy influence
      the fasting plasma glucose, serum adipokines (leptin, adiponectin, resistin) and
      proinflammatory cytokines (interleukin-6, TNF alpha) during 30 and 90 day course.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
